{"tid":2434270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"催淚煙攻入屋 設計師落街掟啤酒罐洩憤被捕 認罪判感化","createTime":"2021-03-05T11:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T14:36:28.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d1440b41b8e5fb4ee829de0f743f9aa9df0ff802","tid":2434270,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"去年5月24日市民於鑼灣發起流水式遊行，反對訂立港區國安法，最終遭警方施放催淚彈驅散。居於區內的設計師，寓所遭催淚煙波及，一怒之下落樓將飲畢的空啤酒罐抛出馬路，被警方拘控以<span class=\"red\">公眾地方擾亂秩序</span>罪。他早前在東區裁判法院認罪，今被判以12個月感化。<br />\n<br />\n辯方大律師求情指，被告李（47歲）居於案發地點樓上的低層單位，因催淚氣體攻入屋內，令他感到呼吸困難兼眼痛，衝動之下持啤酒罐落樓，但他無意圖傷害任何人或破壞財物，亦無意挑釁或鼓動在場人士，而抛出馬路的罐隨即已被駛經車輛輾平。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">羅德泉</span>指，基於控方對辯方的指稱並無異議，法庭接納辯方說法，相信本案屬單一事件，並非有計劃或有預謀，被告亦非參與示威，故判被告接受<span class=\"red\">12個月感化</span>。"},{"pid":"1123a08f93e25a4dfcf39b0b8f42122d48aac9fc","tid":2434270,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/WULDA7S2SFCH3AFB6I4E5RYN2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FWULDA7S2SFCH3AFB6I4E5RYN2A%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=ac548c04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FWULDA7S2SFCH3AFB6I4E5RYN2A%2F&h=76a6d240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/WULDA7S2SFCH3AFB6I4E5RYN2A/</a>"},{"pid":"4cfb0a135bc2c76b65f849a546a61f388189d4a3","tid":2434270,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce8085ca4fbe5b2947f57132522cfa2d43a960f","tid":2434270,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1440b41b8e5fb4ee829de0f743f9aa9df0ff802","tid":2434270,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"去年5月24